        <h1 class="bg-danger">Chardonnay</h1>
        <p>One of the world's most popular grapes, Chardonnay is made in a wide range of styles from lean, sparkling Blanc de Blancs to rich, creamy white wines aged in oak.</p>

    </div>

    <div>
        <h3>PRIMARY FLAVORS</h3>
