    </div>

    <div>
        <h3>HANDLING</h3>
        <img src="~/Content/img/img grapes/handling.png" />
    </div>

    <div>
        <h3>FOOD PAIRING</h3>
        <p>If you keep spice and flavor intensity slightly lower while accentuating creamy, buttery flavors and textures you will be delighted. This is a wine worthy of lobster.</p>
    </div>


</div>
